<h3>Requirements</h3>
<ul>
<li>Qt 5.12 or higher (Qt 5.15+ recommended)</li><li>C++11 capable compiler (MSVC 2017+, GCC 7+, Clang 5+)</li><li>Windows platform: requires linking user32.lib, ole32.lib (needed for error translation)</li>
</ul>

