<div class="green">
<p>After running this example:
- <code>logs/demo.log</code> continuously records all logs in JSON line format.
- The console outputs color-coded logs with an <code>[ID:n]</code> prefix (requires running inside Qt Creator).
- The viewer refreshes in real time, highlighting different levels in different colors.
- Clicking the "Silent WARNING" button produces no dialog.
- Clicking the "Blocking CRITICAL" button shows a modal error box; the program waits until the user confirms.
- The "Simulate Win Error" button automatically translates the system error code into a Chinese description and logs it.</p>
